description:
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen on Ward 50 nephrology to appoint a Ward Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 50 is a 22 bedded ward looking after patients with a variety of renall conditions, and other specialist treatments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates must be able to demonstrate proven leadership and management experience and have previous renal experience. The successful candidate must be highly motivated, innovative and able to lead and manage our inpatient nephrology ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will involve working clinically within the ward, manage a team of staff to deliver a high quality service for our patients whilst recognising the opportunities the lead the team and service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameKaren TimothyJob titleModern MatronEmail addresskaren.timothy@uhcw.nhs.ukTelephone number02476 968310&lt;/p&gt;
